{"tid":326353,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"想去意粉，想問係咪好撚多賊？","createTime":"2017-07-18T02:29:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-21T14:20:02.000Z","uid":5547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4faddd5f9fe029cea814dab45ae3fa2ffaf4f7c1","tid":326353,"uid":5547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T02:29:03.000Z","msg":"Roma Firenze Venezia三個大target<br />\n各三日既話<br />\n係咪羅馬特別危險？ <br />\n<br />\n跟住上奧地利應該就無問題<br />\n<br />\n利申：紅巴 毒遊"},{"pid":"c8cd6206ff4906a056031ec483bf403702c6ae80","tid":326353,"uid":86893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T02:30:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Roma Firenze Venezia三個大target<br />\n各三日既話<br />\n係咪羅馬特別危險？ <br />\n<br />\n跟住上奧地利應該就無問題<br />\n<br />\n利申：紅巴 毒遊</blockquote><br />\n下世好好做人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05ce518425bce283c60ed0f3fce726069f7a3bad","tid":326353,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T02:30:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"271b02293c992f4a012d3ec573400ab1437d298c","tid":326353,"uid":31859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T02:46:36.000Z","msg":"有好多細路扒手 細路喺嗰度好受保護 你見到佢偷嘢又唔打得佢呢樣仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f62a8a54276914f58716b81100d2b86d61d04e99","tid":326353,"uid":60819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T02:52:14.000Z","msg":"岩岩去完歐洲<br />\n法國俾人偷<br />\n意大利無事"},{"pid":"1eaac2ad7315470ea6ce964d049741e21c7aa1a2","tid":326353,"uid":126731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T03:25:51.000Z","msg":"一個人去意粉2轉 (ROME, VEINCE, 米蘭, 五條村, 斜塔, FLORANCE) 都無遇過任何狀況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利伸: 有拖GIP, 相機用A7"},{"pid":"f10b4730002d9ba71380c61fb147517d70da7ace","tid":326353,"uid":97892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T03:29:33.000Z","msg":"剛去完big 4同五漁村，超安全<br />\n遊客多到爆就真<br />\n講危險，巴黎多賊同怪人好多"},{"pid":"7c2fe81e842e55ec85210ee50e9e6b8ce0f673d8","tid":326353,"uid":126731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T03:38:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>剛去完big 4同五漁村，超安全<br />\n遊客多到爆就真<br />\n講危險，巴黎多賊同怪人好多</blockquote><br />\n不過咁,  意粉聽最多係地鐵同火車 掉錢大法分心搶野, 好少話遊客區出事. <br />\n<br />\n聽日講Paris個d真係明搶, 好痴線.  (未去過Paris)"},{"pid":"f12a09effdee69fa68f86b3a368d0b881f4abfc2","tid":326353,"uid":23087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T03:39:50.000Z","msg":"謹慎d就無事<br />\n特別坐車果陣"},{"pid":"01109df072838d3a0294e99aa12f6a690bde78bb","tid":326353,"uid":37631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T03:42:07.000Z","msg":"想放心帶個sceret pocket 啦"},{"pid":"9562e530e4405e9bd5bee201883e8297bdb94d98","tid":326353,"uid":23697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T16:36:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0777b1fa3229ff0dad59de6981c52c02e60505f4","tid":326353,"uid":17104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T18:32:20.000Z","msg":"去左羅馬 五漁村 florence 而家係威尼斯<br />\n暫時都好安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大部分人都好好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我諗米蘭係最危險 因為咁所以我無去<br />\n搭火車去第二個city個陣袋好啲野 用個啲貼身腰包袋住啲錢同passport 應該都無野 同埋個袋放前面 多人就禁實個袋 手機唔好放褲袋 我就一直用手拎住 佢地唔會明搶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e9bb2ca6774c91a1d593a82279145d204c26773","tid":326353,"uid":79185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T19:36:52.000Z","msg":"rome應該係最多小偷<br />\n仲有好多手繩黨簽名黨<br />\nfirenze同venice唔多覺有呢啲呃錢黨<br />\n個人唔好鳩下鳩下就唔會有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 獨毒遊過以上三個地方無穿無爛返黎<br />\n但之前同人去維也納喺地鐵俾人打荷包<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d28d3ac7c9356c3e7f215175bb707605a1124411","tid":326353,"uid":78961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T19:53:02.000Z","msg":"去過冇事<br />\n<br />\n我啲錢分開袋。<br />\n銀包放少少, 褲袋又放十幾二十歐左右<br />\n其他就放喺貼身袋到再用tee shirt遮一遮<br />\n係樣衰啲但安全少少"},{"pid":"c7cce12e51831bfc593cfb6aa501005bf023e407","tid":326353,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T19:53:36.000Z","msg":"做咩相嚟我度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18b56643f513c17e7c8b927385a2df34eaf836a0","tid":326353,"uid":78961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T14:07:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去過冇事<br />\n<br />\n我啲錢分開袋。<br />\n銀包放少少, 褲袋又放十幾二十歐左右<br />\n其他就放喺貼身袋到再用tee shirt遮一遮<br />\n係樣衰啲但安全少少</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同埋有人行埋尼想同你講野，又好似熱心咁幫你，全部都唔好理就得。聽聞咁樣係屈你地俾錢。"},{"pid":"d7533338a261aebd9aca03ad7065324bd4387430","tid":326353,"uid":48358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T14:52:33.000Z","msg":"意粉國地鐘站好多煩膠幫手買飛<br />\n我㩒佢又㩒 講起就慶"},{"pid":"a59b66a703c3740aaada2e92f7aa51d1265a84c6","tid":326353,"uid":76632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T04:49:06.000Z","msg":"我當年係rome feel到有賊偷我野，我電光火石間搶返自己財物，順勢回左一拳。個賊食左我一拳就趁人多逃走，我怕佢有刀或同黨接應，唔敢追，亦都冇報警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n間唔中諗起都覺得自己係懦夫放虎歸山，好內疚，驚個賊繼續作惡。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99202e8d9e6ef246867d0ec77a0ce0ccee032f1b","tid":326353,"uid":86828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T04:52:39.000Z","msg":"係, 重要出左事冇警察會幫你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1237f1e7ca53458703bff32f6fb0cc42f97e390","tid":326353,"uid":24781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T05:03:52.000Z","msg":"羅馬鬥獸場都係啲高危地方"},{"pid":"389114c3445f777d133890771346ec8111a85bf0","tid":326353,"uid":37625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T16:17:02.000Z","msg":"人在Florence ，覺得只要小心啲。啲袋放前面就okay，人地叫你做問卷千萬唔好應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfb0333dc280a9137997731487d19e3a02a84c59","tid":326353,"uid":17104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T18:19:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>意粉國地鐘站好多煩膠幫手買飛<br />\n我㩒佢又㩒 講起就慶</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n之前上網睇話羅馬好多<br />\n但去到又唔覺有<br />\n仲等我次次都拎定岩岩夠數既銀仔出黎買飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bf8bbc0f8d413393aaea2315721e607386a071d","tid":326353,"uid":5547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T18:20:26.000Z","msg":"七日後<br />\n希望死唔去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6c475035b10ed25a09a674e39fad34a7587a43f","tid":326353,"uid":20113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T21:57:29.000Z","msg":"月頭去哂呢三個<br />\n我覺得幾安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"885500d1897861f68f942c3d31d24d23aefa78a8","tid":326353,"uid":70227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T22:00:35.000Z","msg":"係極多<br />\n狼到禁住你係地下打再搶野都會"}]}